# Bus Alert System — Master Project Context

## What This Product Is
Production-grade bus travel alert system for Gujarat, India.
Passengers get automatic call/SMS/WhatsApp alert before their stop.
NOT an MVP — this is a fully production system.

## Live URLs
Frontend:  https://bus-alert-iota.vercel.app
Backend:   https://api-production-e13f.up.railway.app
Health:    https://api-production-e13f.up.railway.app/health

## Infrastructure
Database:  Neon PostgreSQL + PostGIS (AWS Mumbai)
Cache:     Upstash Redis
Backend:   Railway (3 services)
Frontend:  Vercel
Monorepo:  Turborepo + pnpm

## Tech Stack
Mobile:    Flutter (Android only, min SDK 26)
Web:       Next.js 14 App Router + TypeScript
Backend:   Fastify + TypeScript + Drizzle ORM
Database:  PostgreSQL + PostGIS
Realtime:  Socket.IO + Redis Pub/Sub
Maps:      MapMyIndia (Mappls)
Calls:     Exotel
SMS:       MSG91
WhatsApp:  Gupshup
Email OTP: Brevo
Auth:      JWT (15min) + Refresh tokens (30 days)
Validation: Zod
State(web): Zustand + React Query
State(app): Riverpod

