## Environment Variables Needed
Backend (.env.production):
DATABASE_URL, REDIS_URL,
JWT_SECRET, REFRESH_TOKEN_SECRET,
ALERT_PROVIDER, EXOTEL_API_KEY,
EXOTEL_API_TOKEN, EXOTEL_SID,
EXOTEL_CALLER_ID, MSG91_AUTH_KEY,
MSG91_SENDER_ID, MSG91_OTP_TEMPLATE_ID,
BREVO_API_KEY, PORT, NODE_ENV

Web (.env.production):
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL, NEXTAUTH_SECRET,
NEXTAUTH_URL, NODE_ENV

## Important Notes
- Owner cannot see revenue data
- Driver gets conductor permissions 
  ONLY for specific trip after takeover
  NOT globally
- agency_id is nullable (admin + passengers)
- Heartbeat uses in-memory Set to 
  prevent event floods
- GIST indexes on all coordinate columns
- alert fires ONCE per passenger per stop
  never repeats